818
00:35:39.871 --> 00:35:41.248
She was headed up
to the glacier.

819
00:35:41.272 --> 00:35:44.776
You know anything about that?
‐ Let me call the office.

820
00:35:47.278 --> 00:35:48.923
‐ Is everything okay?

821
00:35:48.947 --> 00:35:50.424
‐ Hey. it's John. have you
seen D'arcy at the office?

822
00:35:50.448 --> 00:35:51.692
