843
00:36:30.422 --> 00:36:32.691
‐ Abigail. ‐ Sheriff.

844
00:36:41.533 --> 00:36:43.944
[Erick Serena
and The Killing Floor's

845
00:36:43.968 --> 00:36:46.213
["March of Flames"]

846
00:36:46.237 --> 00:36:48.082
♪ ♪

847
00:36:48.106 --> 00:36:49.717
