857
00:37:16.501 --> 00:37:19.246
♪ No. you ♪

858
00:37:19.270 --> 00:37:23.250
♪ Won't take me down ♪

859
00:37:23.274 --> 00:37:26.377
♪ No. you ♪

860
00:37:28.480 --> 00:37:31.358
‐ See? I told you she'd make it.

861
00:37:31.382 --> 00:37:32.993
Now you're going first.

862
00:37:33.017 --> 00:37:34.295
‐ [grunts] No.

863
00:37:34.319 --> 00:37:37.355
‐ We have to go now. ‐ [coughs]

864
00:37:38.656 --> 00:37:40.434
‐ You're out of time. Harry.

865
00:37:40.458 --> 00:37:43.862
‐ She'll see I am an alien.

866
00:37:45.830 --> 00:37:47.775
‐ No. she won't.

867
00:37:47.799 --> 00:37:51.078
‐ ♪ No. no. no you ♪

868
00:37:51.102 --> 00:37:53.614
‐ [grunts]

869
00:37:53.638 --> 00:37:56.608
‐ ♪ No. no. no you ♪

870
00:37:58.076 --> 00:38:00.387
‐ [grunting]

871
00:38:00.411 --> 00:38:03.524
‐ ♪ No. no. no you ♪

872
00:38:03.548 --> 00:38:06.327
♪ ♪

873
00:38:06.351 --> 00:38:09.521
♪ No. no. no you ♪

874
00:38:13.792 --> 00:38:15.560
‐ [grunts]

875
00:38:22.700 --> 00:38:24.578
‐ Uh. excuse me.

876
00:38:24.602 --> 00:38:26.847
Could pass me some toilet paper?

877
00:38:26.871 --> 00:38:28.273
All out over here.

878
00:38:31.075 --> 00:38:33.387
Oh. thank you.

879
00:38:33.411 --> 00:38:35.356
[toilet flushes] [sighs]

880
00:38:35.380 --> 00:38:38.826
Thank you so much.
You're a lifesaver.

881
00:38:38.850 --> 00:38:40.795
‐ Us ladies have
to stick together. right?

882
00:38:40.819 --> 00:38:42.563
You live in town?

883
00:38:42.587 --> 00:38:44.865
‐ Yeah. just down the road.

884
00:38:44.889 --> 00:38:47.334
My husband's the mayor. ‐ Wow.

885
00:38:47.358 --> 00:38:49.603
I just moved here.
I don't know anybody.

886
00:38:49.627 --> 00:38:52.006
‐ Oh. well. you should
take my number.

887
00:38:52.030 --> 00:38:53.374
[ominous music]

888
00:38:53.398 --> 00:38:56.010
Feel free to pick my brain.
Here you go.

889
00:38:56.034 --> 00:38:57.545
I'm Kate Hawthorne.

890
00:38:57.569 --> 00:38:59.780
‐ Kate. That's my sister's name.

891
00:38:59.804 --> 00:39:02.016
Sarah Houston.
Thanks for the number.

892
00:39:02.040 --> 00:39:04.251
I'll be sure to use it.
‐ Call anytime.

893
00:39:04.275 --> 00:39:05.452
