894
00:39:05.476 --> 00:39:07.121
‐ Okay. gotta go
relieve the babysitter.

895
00:39:07.145 --> 00:39:08.656
‐ Oh. you have kids?

896
00:39:08.680 --> 00:39:11.492
‐ Oh. just one.
We have a little boy named Max.

897
00:39:11.516 --> 00:39:14.495
‐ Max. that's wonderful.

898
00:39:14.519 --> 00:39:15.896
‐ Nice to meet you.

899
00:39:15.920 --> 00:39:22.894
♪ ♪

900
00:39:29.601 --> 00:39:32.437
[engine rumbling]

901
00:39:34.639 --> 00:39:36.050
