907
00:39:48.553 --> 00:39:51.899
Where the hell are you?
I'm coming to get you.

908
00:39:51.923 --> 00:39:53.367
‐ I'm okay. Dad!

909
00:39:53.391 --> 00:39:55.636
Don't ask questions.
