912
00:40:00.398 --> 00:40:02.509
‐ [gurgles] ‐ Oh. God.

913
00:40:02.533 --> 00:40:04.478
‐ ♪ The height of a giant ♪

914
00:40:04.502 --> 00:40:08.482
‐ ♪ Or the will
of a great chief's son ♪

915
00:40:08.506 --> 00:40:10.684
♪ But I'm somewhere
in the middle ♪

916
00:40:10.708 --> 00:40:13.654
♪ With my feet slippin' off
the pedals ♪

917
00:40:13.678 --> 00:40:15.322
‐ How is he? ‐ Not good.

918
00:40:15.346 --> 00:40:17.024
Go get help. Go get help!

919
00:40:17.048 --> 00:40:18.559
‐ Okay.

920
00:40:18.583 --> 00:40:20.494
‐ ♪ And my silence turned
to thoughts ♪

921
00:40:20.518 --> 00:40:22.463
♪ Am I in constant disbelief ♪

922
00:40:22.487 --> 00:40:24.365
♪ That which I teach.
through my teeth ♪

923
00:40:24.389 --> 00:40:26.934
♪ Becomes what I preach ♪

924
00:40:26.958 --> 00:40:28.969
♪ Oh. I sure would
like to live ♪

925
00:40:28.993 --> 00:40:31.705
♪ Without the burden
of commitment ♪

926
00:40:31.729 --> 00:40:35.943
♪ Not attached to any person.
place. or thing ♪

927
00:40:35.967 --> 00:40:38.145
‐ Hurry. He's out here.

928
00:40:38.169 --> 00:40:40.180
‐ ♪ To carry nowhere alone ♪

929
00:40:40.204 --> 00:40:41.749
‐ What the hell?

930
00:40:41.773 --> 00:40:43.651
‐ ♪ I am hopeful but tiring ♪

931
00:40:43.675 --> 00:40:45.786
‐ Asta!

932
00:40:45.810 --> 00:40:47.187
‐ Asta?

933
00:40:47.211 --> 00:40:49.590
‐ ♪ Because some of us
are ghost embodied ♪

934
00:40:49.614 --> 00:40:52.092
‐ Asta. are you here?

935
00:40:52.116 --> 00:40:54.795
‐ ♪ In the flesh ♪

936
00:40:54.819 --> 00:40:57.398
♪ What you saw was
a reflection of a moment ♪

937
00:40:57.422 --> 00:40:59.433
‐ Asta.
what the hell's going on?

938
00:40:59.457 --> 00:41:02.736
‐ ♪ It was never really
ever there ♪

939
00:41:02.760 --> 00:41:05.272
‐ Hey. Dad. ‐ Hell no.

940
00:41:05.296 --> 00:41:06.931
‐ Ah!

941
00:41:09.033 --> 00:41:10.635
Dad.

942
00:41:12.303 --> 00:41:14.548
‐ What are you doing
hanging with that thing?

943
00:41:14.572 --> 00:41:16.550
‐ Do you know
what that thing is?

944
00:41:16.574 --> 00:41:19.053
‐ Well. it's violating
a whole bunch of health codes.

945
00:41:19.077 --> 00:41:20.654
I know that for sure.

946
00:41:20.678 --> 00:41:23.657
‐ Can you just say it.
so there's no confusion?

947
00:41:23.681 --> 00:41:26.493
‐ Why's there an alien
in my freezer?

948
00:41:26.517 --> 00:41:27.761
‐ Yes. okay. ‐ Asta?

949
00:41:27.785 --> 00:41:28.929
‐ Mm‐hmm.

950
00:41:28.953 --> 00:41:32.032
The cold slows the bleeding.

951
00:41:32.056 --> 00:41:33.734
and he's not just an alien.

952
00:41:33.758 --> 00:41:35.569
and the alien
is someone we know.

953
00:41:35.593 --> 00:41:37.938
‐ The mayor. I knew it.

954
00:41:37.962 --> 00:41:40.407
‐ No. Dad. It's Harry.

955
00:41:40.431 --> 00:41:42.333
‐ The doctor's an alien?

956
00:41:43.234 --> 00:41:46.080
And you wanted me to get a
yearly checkup from that thing.

957
00:41:46.104 --> 00:41:47.915
‐ [grunts]

958
00:41:47.939 --> 00:41:49.616
[sighs]

959
00:41:49.640 --> 00:41:53.287
I allowed myself
to become too human.

960
00:41:53.311 --> 00:41:55.456
That's why I couldn't

961
00:41:55.480 --> 00:41:57.891
complete my mission.

962
00:41:57.915 --> 00:42:00.661
It's my fault.

963
00:42:00.685 --> 00:42:01.895
[moans]

964
00:42:01.919 --> 00:42:04.164
‐ If I don't do something.
he will die.

965
00:42:04.188 --> 00:42:05.566
I need your help.

966
00:42:05.590 --> 00:42:07.067
‐ Dan. you back there?

967
00:42:07.091 --> 00:42:08.602
‐ Shit.

968
00:42:08.626 --> 00:42:11.872
‐ I'll take care of it.
Be right there!

969
00:42:11.896 --> 00:42:13.207
Can we trust that creature?

970
00:42:13.231 --> 00:42:16.377
‐ He's in trouble.
and we can help.

971
00:42:16.401 --> 00:42:19.046
‐ I don't like it. but
if you believe in him. okay.

972
00:42:19.070 --> 00:42:21.348
‐ Okay. Thank you.

973
00:42:21.372 --> 00:42:24.685
‐ Just move him‐‐
it away from the fish.

974
00:42:24.709 --> 00:42:26.511
‐ Okay.

975
00:42:27.578 --> 00:42:28.822
‐ How you doing. Sheriff?

976
00:42:28.846 --> 00:42:31.358
‐ I'm good.
I saw your truck out front.

977
00:42:31.382 --> 00:42:32.626
I just wanted to make sure

978
00:42:32.650 --> 00:42:34.461
