You know. Asta's a strong woman.

980
00:42:36.020 --> 00:42:37.464
She'll be fine.

981
00:42:37.488 --> 00:42:40.534
Let's just wait out the storm
and fire up some burgers.

982
00:42:40.558 --> 00:42:41.935
‐ Ha! Haven't you heard?
They're back.

983
00:42:41.959 --> 00:42:43.771
Doctor got in an accident;

984
