Asta had to take him
to Braddock for an MRI.

985
00:42:47.932 --> 00:42:49.543
‐ Really?

986
00:42:49.567 --> 00:42:51.569
Well. good. That's‐‐that's good.

987
00:42:54.038 --> 00:42:55.282
You all right. Dan?

988
00:42:55.306 --> 00:42:56.950
You like you done
seen a ghost or something.

989
00:42:56.974 --> 00:43:00.120
‐ I'm okay.
I guess it's the worry.

990
00:43:00.144 --> 00:43:02.623
‐ Right.

991
00:43:02.647 --> 00:43:05.283
All right. then. Well. night.

992
00:43:06.617 --> 00:43:08.128
Stand down on the search.

993
00:43:08.152 --> 00:43:10.330
They made it down
off the mountain.

994
00:43:10.354 --> 00:43:12.132
‐ Copy that. Sheriff.
We'll notify.

995
00:43:12.156 --> 00:43:14.134
‐ Harry. Oh. God.

996
00:43:14.158 --> 00:43:15.569
Harry. wake up.

997
00:43:15.593 --> 00:43:17.004
Harry. you are getting worse.

998
00:43:17.028 --> 00:43:19.573
Tell me how to help you.

999
00:43:19.597 --> 00:43:21.975
‐ Without my radio. it's over.

1000
00:43:21.999 --> 00:43:23.577
[dramatic music]

1001
00:43:23.601 --> 00:43:24.812
Let me die.

1002
00:43:24.836 --> 00:43:27.014
‐ No.

1003
00:43:27.038 --> 00:43:28.549
Harry. wait.

1004
00:43:28.573 --> 00:43:30.350
Look.

1005
00:43:30.374 --> 00:43:32.119
You can help us now.

1006
00:43:32.143 --> 00:43:33.387
‐ [gasps]

1007
00:43:33.411 --> 00:43:34.988
♪ ♪

1008
00:43:35.012 --> 00:43:36.757
You found it.

1009
