‐ [sighs] Yeah.

1010
00:43:39.016 --> 00:43:40.394
‐ If she knew
what she was giving me.

1011
00:43:40.418 --> 00:43:42.329
she would let me die. [grunts]

1012
00:43:42.353 --> 00:43:44.131
‐ Tell me how to help you.

1013
00:43:44.155 --> 00:43:45.466
‐ My leg.

1014
00:43:45.490 --> 00:43:47.701
It's poisoning me.

1015
00:43:47.725 --> 00:43:51.338
I will die
if you don't chop it off.

1016
00:43:51.362 --> 00:43:52.806
‐ We need to do what?

1017
00:43:52.830 --> 00:43:56.143
‐ You heard him.
Grab the meat cleaver.

1018
00:43:56.167 --> 00:43:58.445
‐ Aah!

1019
00:43:58.469 --> 00:44:01.081
‐ Uh. it's okay.
It's gonna be okay.

1020
00:44:01.105 --> 00:44:02.783
All right. ‐ [moans]

1021
00:44:02.807 --> 00:44:04.718
‐ Okay.

1022
00:44:04.742 --> 00:44:06.520
Harry.

1023
00:44:06.544 --> 00:44:09.089
It's gonna be all right.

1024
00:44:09.113 --> 00:44:11.592
I'm sorry.

1025
00:44:11.616 --> 00:44:14.328
[suspenseful music]

1026
00:44:14.352 --> 00:44:16.530
God. I can't do it.

1027
00:44:16.554 --> 00:44:17.731
‐ I can.

1028
00:44:17.755 --> 00:44:20.134
‐ Okay. okay. okay. I'm sorry.

1029
00:44:20.158 --> 00:44:23.270
Oh. my... ‐ I'm scared.

1030
00:44:23.294 --> 00:44:25.305
[dramatic music]

1031
00:44:25.329 --> 00:44:26.874
‐ Okay. look at me.

1032
00:44:26.898 --> 00:44:28.475
I'm right here.

1033
00:44:28.499 --> 00:44:30.277
I won't let you die.

1034
00:44:30.301 --> 00:44:32.880
♪ ♪

1035
00:44:32.904 --> 00:44:34.248
‐ I believe her.

1036
00:44:34.272 --> 00:44:38.051
No one's dying today.
but now I have my device.

1037
00:44:38.075 --> 00:44:40.478
so how about tomorrow?

1038
00:44:41.579 --> 00:44:44.291
All eight billion of them.

1039
00:44:44.315 --> 00:44:47.418
‐ [grunts] ‐ Aah!

1040
00:44:49.086 --> 00:44:52.032
[mysterious music]

